/* Intel 82077A (8272A compatible) floppy controller */

/* This module expects the following functions to be defined
 * elsewhere: 
 * 
 * inb()
 * outb()
 * floppyexec()
 * floppyeject() 
 * floppysetup0()
 * floppysetup1()
 * dmainit()
 * dmasetup()
 * dmaend()
 * 
 * On DMA systems, floppyexec() should be an empty function; 
